          "notes": "Annual filing window opens February 1 and closes April 30; the fixed date models the April 30 deadline. Applicability requires carriesWorkersComp = false (the 406.004 non-subscriber election is what triggers the FORM) AND employeeCount >= 1. The employeeCount leaf approximates the form's 'one or more employees who are NOT EXEMPT from workers' compensation coverage' - exempt classes (certain domestic, farm/ranch workers) are not modeled, which is implausible as a venue's entire workforce (UNVER-2). The 406.005 posting duty is NOT folded here - it reaches every employer and is encoded as tx-venue-wc-coverage-notice (SPLIT-3 corrected the earlier note that wrongly projected 406.004's non-subscriber gate onto 406.005)."
        }
